title: UPSC IES/ISS result 2015 announced; check upsc.gov.in
text:
UPSC IES/ISS result 2015: Union Public Service Commission (UPSC) announced the written examination results of the Indian Economic Service(IES) and India Statistical Service (ISS) today (i.e. 27th August). Candidates can check the final result on the official website upsc.gov.in .
Arushi Kaushik has topped the IES Examination followed by Arshee Khosla who secured second rank and Ruby Rani who hitched the third position whereas Dona Francis clinched the first position in the ISS Examination.
Click here to check UPSC IES/ISS 2015 result
The written test was held in May and interview for personality test was conducted in August 2015 by the UPSC.The commission has selected 14 candidates (Gen: 8, OBC: 3, SC: 2, ST: 1) for IES and 50 (Gen: 25, OBC: 12, SC: 8, ST: 5) for ISS.
The marks of the candidates will be available on the official website within 15 days from the date of publication of result.
Note: For any information regarding the examination, the candidates may contact on 011-23385271 between 10 am to to 5 pm.
